short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Resolve GUIDs from a unity project to their asset names

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A tool that helps you to get information on GUIDs for your project directly in the browser - Useful for PR reviews and projects that have a lot of ScriptableObjects and Prefabs to understand what is linked in the assets.
This project is open source and can be found on github: https://github.com/JohannesDeml/unity-guid-resolver
